org.xmlsoft

Class SAXHandlerEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xmlsoft.SAXHandlerEngine

  • public class SAXHandlerEngine
extends Object

    Bridge class between SAXHandler and native JNI module.

    This class is NOT thread safe. Most methods are invoked by JNI functions.

    Author:
    Jang-Ho Hwang, rath@xrath.com
